- @body_id = 'Acquisitions'
%title
  Acquisitions | TULA

#acquisitions_container
  #acquisitions_year_select
    %h1
      %h3
        Year:
        %select
          %option{:value => 2014, :selected => true} 
            2014
          %option{:value => 2013}
            2013
  #2013_acquisitions.acquisition_year
    %h1
      2013 Acquired Companies
    %p.acquisition_subheader
      Schedule of companies invested in that have been acquired since the start of 2013
    %table.why_table.acquisitions_table
      %tr
        %th Company
        %th Price at 1/1/13
        %th Buy Out Price
        %th Return
      - a = Acquisition.where(:year => 2013).order(:id).all
      - a.each do |i|
        %tr
          %td
            #{i.company}
          %td
            #{number_to_currency(i.initial_price, :unit => "$", :precision => 2)}
          %td
            #{number_to_currency(i.acquisition_price, :unit => "$", :precision => 2)}
          %td
            #{((i.return)*100).round(1)}%
    #acquisition_notes
      %p.why_dislosure
        * On 6/10/13, the deal for the buy out of Virgin Media by Liberty Global was completed. Virgin Media shareholders received $17.50 for each share they owned plus stock in Liberty Global. Total return including both cash payments and receipt of Liberty Global stock equates to a 35% return over the 1/1/13 valuation.
  #2014_acquisitions.acquisition_year
    %h1
      2014 Acquired Companies
    %p.acquisition_subheader
      Schedule of companies invested in that have been acquired since the start of 2014
    %table.why_table.acquisitions_table
      %tr
        %th Company
        %th Price at 1/1/14
        %th Buy Out Price
        %th Return
      - a = Acquisition.where(:year => 2014).order(:id).all
      - a.each do |i|
        %tr
          %td
            #{i.company}
          %td
            #{number_to_currency(i.initial_price, :unit => "$", :precision => 2)}
          %td
            #{number_to_currency(i.acquisition_price, :unit => "$", :precision => 2)}
          %td
            #{((i.return)*100).round(1)}%
    #acquisition_notes
      %p.why_dislosure
        

